  "prompt": "What is a good place to learn singing in hyderabad?",
  "response": "Hyderabad offers several reputable places where you can learn singing. Here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Shankar Mahadevan Academy**: Renowned for its structured courses and extensive curriculum spanning various genres of music.\n\n2. **Raga & Rhythm Music Academy**: Known for its experienced faculty and personalized lessons tailored to individual needs.\n\n3. **Sangeet Sadhana School of Music**: Offers training in both Hindustani and Carnatic vocal music, along with opportunities to perform.\n\n4. **Kaladarbar Music Academy**: Provides comprehensive training in classical music and various other genres, with performance opportunities.\n\n5. **SaPa (Subramaniam Academy of Performing Arts)**: Founded by renowned musicians, offering high-quality music education and certifications.\n\n6. **Surmandal Music Academy**: Focuses on both classical and contemporary music, with opportunities for group and solo singing.\n\nBefore committing, it is a good idea to visit these places, meet the instructors, and possibly take trial lessons to find the best fit for your learning style and requirements.",
